snippet.title: Tombwater World Exclusive Reveal Trailer – PC Gaming Show: Most Wanted 2024
snippet.description:
A top-down, retro-styled soulslike western, Tombwater sees players battling mutant wolves and Cthulhu-ish cowboys with revolvers, magic and cactus batons.
